                config MCUX_COMPONENT_component.wifi_bt_module.board_rd_rw61x
                    bool "NXP RD-RW61x"
                    help
                        The RW612 is a highly integrated, low-power tri-radio wireless MCU with
                        an integrated MCU and Wi-Fi® 6 + Bluetooth® Low Energy (LE) 5.4 / 802.15.4
                        radios designed for a broad array of applications, including connected smart
                        home devices, enterprise and industrial automation, smart accessories and
                        smart energy.

                        Detailed information about RD-RW61x-BGA board you can find on
                        https://www.nxp.com/part/RW612ET
