                    bool "NXP UBX-JODY-W2-USD"
                    help
                        JODY-W2 is a compact module based on the NXP 88W8987 AEC-Q100 compliant chipset.
                        It enables Wi-Fi, Bluetooth EDR, and Bluetooth low energy communications, and is
                        thus ideal for in-vehicle infotainment and telematics, industrial applications
                        such as machine control, and other applications requiring high data rates.
                        The module is built to meet the requirements for operation in very high temperatures,
                        such as telematics systems in cars. JODY-W2 supports 1x1 single-antenna 802.11ac
                        Wi-Fi operation, with data rates up to 433 Mbit/s.

                        Detailed information about Jody module you can find on
                        https://www.u-blox.com/en/product/jody-w2-series

